    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "At the entrance of #m10001000#, I met #p402#'s father #p202#, the chief of #m10001000#. He was even more blunt and difficult to talk to than I'd anticipated, but I finally convinced him to accept #p402# back with open arms. I also got #p402#'s late mother's #b#t4031006##k as proof. Now, all I need to do is get this watch to #p402# in #m10003000#."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I gave #p402# his late mother's #b#t4031006##k. As a sign of appreciation, he gave me an earring he received from friends he met while traveling. Well, #p202# forgave #p402#, but it doesn't seem like #p402# plans to head home right away. Maybe I should keep an eye open next time I'm in #m10001000#."
    },
